data.description: Back on the market and reduced $25,000!  Introducing an ideal opportunity for investors, farmers, or home buying enthusiasts! This property provides the perfect canvas for customization and expansion. It hosts a variety of appealing features, including one division right, a shop, and a loafing shed. What sets this property apart is a unique section of the home that comes with its own separate entrance and deck, previously utilized as a beauty salon. With the ability to be closed off from the main section of the home, this space presents a multitude of possibilities for repurposing. There is a nice built in hot tub on the back deck for relaxing after a long day. While the property is being sold as is, it holds incredible potential for those with a vision to transform this diamond in the rough into a stunning home. The canvas is open for creativity, offering numerous possibilities to add value through personalized finishes and enhancements. This is an opportunity not to be missed for those seeking a versatile and promising property.  *Agents please see private info for additional details. *
